## filter-fragments/base.filter

#######################
## Wisdom and Portal ##
#######################

Show
  BaseType "Scroll of Wisdom"
  ##ScrollOfWisdomText
  Continue

Show
  BaseType "Portal Scroll"
  ##PortalScrollText
  Continue

Hide # Red Maps
  BaseType "Scroll of Wisdom" "Portal Scroll"
  Class "Currency"
  AreaLevel > 77
  StackSize < 10
  ##CurrencyBorder
  ##DefaultBackground
  SetFontSize 45

Hide # White-Yellow Maps
  BaseType "Scroll of Wisdom" "Portal Scroll"
  Class "Currency"
  AreaLevel > 67
  StackSize < 6
  ##CurrencyBorder
  ##DefaultBackground
  SetFontSize 45

Show # Red Maps
  BaseType "Scroll of Wisdom" "Portal Scroll"
  Class "Currency"
  ##CurrencyBorder
  ##DefaultBackground
  SetFontSize 40
  MinimapIcon 0 Grey Raindrop

